Revision history for Fuse::TagLayer

0.12	2013-12-09
	- backends are modular now
	- new option: --backend
	- pure Perl backend

0.11	unreleased
	- enforce current min. tag-length of 2 for all tag-sources
	- new option: --ignore-numbers-only
	- Changes file
	- typos fixed, rephrasing in pod, elaborated
	- assume xattribs to be in utf8, and decode
	- repository metadata in Makefile.PL

0.10	2013-02-17
	- CPAN compatible README and tiny POD tweak

0.09	2013-02-13
	First public version, released on an unsuspecting world.
